    "title": "Avoid large strings",
    "tutorial": "/quick-guides/document/introduction.md",
    "content": [
      {
        "id": "bigStrings-1",
        "type": "span",
        "value": "If you are working with long strings you may need to retrieve parts or split them to handle in your application. Consider modeling your data using hashes or JSON. Both data structures provide fast and efficient data retrieval via the "
      },
      {
        "id": "bigStrings-2",
        "type": "link",
        "value": {
          "href": "https://redis.io/docs/stack/search/?utm_source=redisinsight&utm_medium=recommendation&utm_campaign=bigStrings/",
          "name": "query and search capabilities"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "bigStrings-3",
        "type": "span",
        "value": ", natively developed in Redis, and available as part of Redis Stack, Redis Enterprise Cloud, and Redis Enterprise Software."
