  "integersInSets": {
    "id": "integersInSets",
    "redisStack": true,
    "title": "Use only integers in sets to improve memory efficiency",
    "tutorial": "/quick-guides/document/working-with-hashes.md",
    "content": [
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-1",
        "type": "paragraph",
        "value": "Sets that contain only integers are extremely efficient memory-wise. Try to use integers by mapping string identifiers to integers by either using enums in your programming language or using a Redis hash data structure to map values to integers."
      },
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-2",
        "type": "spacer",
        "value": "l"
      },
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-3",
        "type": "paragraph",
        "value": "Once you switch to integers, Redis uses the IntSet encoding internally."
      },
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-4",
        "type": "spacer",
        "value": "l"
      },
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-5",
        "type": "paragraph",
        "value": "The IntSet encoding is extremely memory efficient. By default, the value of `set-max-intset-entries` is 512 and is configurable in redis.conf. However, increasing this value will lead to an increase in the latency of set operations and CPU utilization."
      },
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-6",
        "type": "spacer",
        "value": "l"
      },
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-7",
        "type": "span",
        "value": "Run "
      },
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-8",
        "type": "link",
        "value": {
          "href": "https://redis.io/commands/info/?utm_source=redisinsight&utm_medium=recommendation&utm_campaign=integersInSets/",
          "name": "INFO COMMANDSTATS"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-9",
        "type": "span",
        "value": " before and after making this change to verify the latency numbers."
      },
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-10",
        "type": "spacer",
        "value": "l"
      },
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-11",
        "type": "span",
        "value": "See the "
      },
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-12",
        "type": "link",
        "value": {
          "href": "https://redis.io/docs/management/optimization/memory-optimization/?utm_source=redisinsight&utm_medium=recommendation&utm_campaign=integersInSets/",
          "name": "documentation"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "integersInSets-13",
        "type": "span",
        "value": " for more memory optimization strategies."
      }
    ]
  },
